name: ExtensionInsurancePlan_Coverage
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.InsurancePlan.coverage` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `InsurancePlan.coverage` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `InsurancePlan.coverage` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`InsurancePlan.coverage` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `InsurancePlan.coverage` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4B: `InsurancePlan.coverage` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4: `InsurancePlan.coverage` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Following are the generation technical comments:
Element `InsurancePlan.coverage` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `InsurancePlan.coverage`, but has no comparisons.
